1. Supertonic TTS model — OpenRAIL-M
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The narration is synthesized with the Supertonic ONNX model, licensed under
OpenRAIL-M. Commercial use and YouTube monetization are permitted, but you MUST
disclose that the audio is AI-generated (OpenRAIL-M Attachment A (e)).
`/publish-kit` inserts this into the description and end card:

    이 영상의 내레이션은 AI 음성 합성(Supertonic)으로 제작되었습니다.
    Narration generated by AI voice synthesis (Supertonic).

Obtain the model and review its license/model card before commercial use. The
model weights are downloaded at first run into ~/.cache/supertonic3/ and are NOT
redistributed in this repository.

