------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3. Stock media — Pexels / Unsplash / Pixabay
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Fetched at build time via each provider's API using your own keys (.env).
Attribution is courtesy rather than a strict legal requirement, but `/publish-kit`
appends compact photographer credits. Review each provider's license for your use.
No stock binaries are committed to this repository.

